{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019PBWgdg2iaSzAxriQU3y3B","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 300-referral-system\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-24T21:27:27Z — OK\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: [backend] Database migration `011_referral.sql`\n    12→**Status**: Done\n    13→**Changes**:\n    14→- Created `services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql` with all 5 referral tables:\n    15→  - `referral_codes` — one code per wallet (UNIQUE on wallet + code)\n    16→  - `referral_links` — immutable referrer binding (UNIQUE on referee_wallet)\n    17→  - `referral_earnings` — per-game earnings with idempotency guard (UNIQUE on referee_wallet + round_id)\n    18→  - `referral_claims` — async payout tracking with status CHECK constraint (pending/processing/completed/failed)\n    19→  - `referral_kol_rates` — KOL custom rates (wallet PK)\n    20→- Indexes: referrer/referee wallet lookups on earnings, round_id, claims by wallet+date, partial index on pending/processing claims, referrer_wallet on links\n    21→- Follows existing migration patterns (IF NOT EXISTS, TIMESTAMPTZ, BIGINT for lamports, no foreign keys)\n    22→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n    23→**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n    24→\n    25→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-24T21:41:16Z\n    26→- **Result**: Gap analysis report generated\n    27→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    28→- **Log**: gap-analysis.log\n    29→\n    30→## Iteration 2 — 2026-03-25T08:54:27Z — FALSE DONE (rejected retroactively)\n    31→- **Agent claimed DONE** but only the migration was complete. Checklist was refined between runs.\n    32→- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    33→\n    34→## Iteration 3 — 2026-03-25T09:09:19Z — OK\n    35→\n    36→**Item**: [backend] DB client methods in `db.ts`: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode` for code CRUD\n    37→**Status**: Done\n    38→**Changes**:\n    39→- Added `ReferralCode` interface to type section (id, wallet, code, created_at, updated_at)\n    40→- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode`\n    41→- Implemented all 4 methods in `createDb()`:\n    42→  - `insertReferralCode`: INSERT with RETURNING *\n    43→  - `getReferralCodeByWallet`: SELECT by wallet, returns undefined if not found\n    44→  - `getReferralCodeByCode`: SELECT by code, returns undefined if not found\n    45→  - `upsertReferralCode`: INSERT ON CONFLICT (wallet) DO UPDATE — replaces code for existing wallet\n    46→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n    47→**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n    48→\n    49→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25T09:26:04Z\n    50→- **Result**: Gap analysis report updated (post-iteration-3)\n    51→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    52→- **Totals**: 15 SATISFIED, 0 DEFERRED, 75 GAP (90 total criteria)\n    53→\n    54→## Fix — 2026-03-25 — Loop false-DONE guard added\n    55→- **Problem**: Agent output `<promise>DONE</promise>` after completing 1 item, loop script accepted without verifying remaining count\n    56→- **Fix**: `spec-loop.sh` now checks `count_remaining` before accepting DONE signal. False DONE is logged and loop continues.\n    57→- **Spec update**: Referral codes changed to always be player-chosen (3-16 chars, `[a-z0-9-]`). No auto-generation.\n    58→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c89a03cc-8748-4b08-a745-25648f76e1cb","uuid":"ce948b3b-a7f1-48fb-9d1c-88abb0fa2bac","timestamp":"2026-03-25T10:19:29.778Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/history.md","content":"# Implementation History — 300-referral-system\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-24T21:27:27Z — OK\n\n**Item**: [backend] Database migration `011_referral.sql`\n**Status**: Done\n**Changes**:\n- Created `services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql` with all 5 referral tables:\n  - `referral_codes` — one code per wallet (UNIQUE on wallet + code)\n  - `referral_links` — immutable referrer binding (UNIQUE on referee_wallet)\n  - `referral_earnings` — per-game earnings with idempotency guard (UNIQUE on referee_wallet + round_id)\n  - `referral_claims` — async payout tracking with status CHECK constraint (pending/processing/completed/failed)\n  - `referral_kol_rates` — KOL custom rates (wallet PK)\n- Indexes: referrer/referee wallet lookups on earnings, round_id, claims by wallet+date, partial index on pending/processing claims, referrer_wallet on links\n- Follows existing migration patterns (IF NOT EXISTS, TIMESTAMPTZ, BIGINT for lamports, no foreign keys)\n**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n\n## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-24T21:41:16Z\n- **Result**: Gap analysis report generated\n- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n- **Log**: gap-analysis.log\n\n## Iteration 2 — 2026-03-25T08:54:27Z — FALSE DONE (rejected retroactively)\n- **Agent claimed DONE** but only the migration was complete. Checklist was refined between runs.\n- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n\n## Iteration 3 — 2026-03-25T09:09:19Z — OK\n\n**Item**: [backend] DB client methods in `db.ts`: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode` for code CRUD\n**Status**: Done\n**Changes**:\n- Added `ReferralCode` interface to type section (id, wallet, code, created_at, updated_at)\n- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode`\n- Implemented all 4 methods in `createDb()`:\n  - `insertReferralCode`: INSERT with RETURNING *\n  - `getReferralCodeByWallet`: SELECT by wallet, returns undefined if not found\n  - `getReferralCodeByCode`: SELECT by code, returns undefined if not found\n  - `upsertReferralCode`: INSERT ON CONFLICT (wallet) DO UPDATE — replaces code for existing wallet\n**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n\n## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25T09:26:04Z\n- **Result**: Gap analysis report updated (post-iteration-3)\n- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n- **Totals**: 15 SATISFIED, 0 DEFERRED, 75 GAP (90 total criteria)\n\n## Fix — 2026-03-25 — Loop false-DONE guard added\n- **Problem**: Agent output `<promise>DONE</promise>` after completing 1 item, loop script accepted without verifying remaining count\n- **Fix**: `spec-loop.sh` now checks `count_remaining` before accepting DONE signal. False DONE is logged and loop continues.\n- **Spec update**: Referral codes changed to always be player-chosen (3-16 chars, `[a-z0-9-]`). No auto-generation.\n","numLines":58,"startLine":1,"totalLines":58}}}
